{"title":"那个古老的回乡","authors":["姚欣则"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个古老的回乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姚欣则  回族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土塬上那个古老的回乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎依然沉浸在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠远的梦中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若断若续的思绪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄索绕在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清真寺塔尖的新月上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和黄土地一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质朴厚重的回民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把浓浓的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入贫瘠的土壤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热土便有了跳动的心律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾吐出慈母般的亲情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老与新生、梦幻与现实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞击着沉重的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻化为崭新的意识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汩汩流淌在回乡的晚上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阒寂的小村也按捺不住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴求和遐想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从历史的积淀中升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染绿了泛黄的岁月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}